{"tid":1310191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PETITION 去白宮其實作用不大","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T11:17:01.000Z","uid":269641,"like":72,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4ae8c9ebda3cbf85b6f0c0c43bc613a54c38bd","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"請大家幫忙宣傳以下重點：<br />\n<br />\n（1）美國三權分立，用黎打大佬的&ldquo; 香港自由人權法&rdquo; 法案並非來自白宮。住美國者（任何身份）或海外美僑應該寫信去國會議員推，而非去白宮請願。<br />\n<br />\n（2) 以下這個四大組織的ActionNetwork連結是專業發信網站，輸入地址即找出所屬三名議員，可輕易編輯信函內容，一次就寄出三封信。<br />\n<br />\n呼籲你D 美國朋友 親戚 總之有美國地址 幫手去新區議員 代表去支持依件事！！！！<br />\n好簡單 - 放入 美國地址後自動揾到個區同議會代表。用已寫好的信 （或自己執筆寫一封）要求代表支持 <br />\n<br />\n&quot;H.R.3289 - Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act of 2019&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=cad4693c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無國會議員支持 成個香港人權法案就會胎死腹中！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜家就正正係咁情況 - 法案已經各自在參、眾兩院提出，目前是小組委員會審議階段。雖然獲跨黨派支持，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但至今眾議院只有9個共同提案人，而參議院就有8個。若法案在只有少數議員關注的情況下，就會像2017年提案一樣，胎死腹中。</span><br />\n<br />\n要令到法案得到高度關注，加速審議進度，就需要得到更多國會議員加入成為共同提案人。需要結合力量，再向議員進行游說。法案的共同提案人越多，就越能更快重新提交大會表決通過。"},{"pid":"df17d22dbce20d84643894c924d73724085e0d71","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d65875e0534a97f90c9bf158453597287d721fff","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1de14d24e5a0750f792b1f920df75639665a7725","tid":1310191,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1c748437d1da742130d726d216fc353e53e50f","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f45f6f7438e4e895b3f6623ef195a40b6e27ef26","tid":1310191,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4de4397cb3dd99916c600eec42c5c2ecd720d0","tid":1310191,"uid":9348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"莫以善少而不為"},{"pid":"3f23516cf33ea0d5727c5b3733cda80d38d34332","tid":1310191,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f4de4397cb3dd99916c600eec42c5c2ecd720d0","tid":1310191,"uid":9348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"莫以善少而不為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"當然搵到美國親朋就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c1dd3f098416e69d38f17911e295ff5d3ce8ba","tid":1310191,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n<br />\n[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad5b9ade12c06490e2f7e7e243816e55ec6ef5ea","tid":1310191,"uid":272458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"差d負評左你"},{"pid":"a4dd3ce4b8dc07857f7a47496301bf24dcd87265","tid":1310191,"uid":5172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c3458617664d4000217673696337fcefc9bbb6","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e1160f1fa3392084b768ef876be4d960057f9b","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db95d7f407ee724c77058b3cd8fc17994306f845","tid":1310191,"uid":266172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"作用不大都要做，而你講的更加要做。"},{"pid":"8662dd28904810acad9b47f50895fa8a3cb25595","tid":1310191,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf383fae9c49f96ad3a33e69e58b93bd3e374f70","tid":1310191,"uid":79744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f6322b763eaf6ffd3a8a604ef3988b5d0e8e88b","tid":1310191,"uid":74363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實總議員同參議員分別要幾多人先可以move?"},{"pid":"592329c6769f8b4b629b0d0b9b03149841fafa92","tid":1310191,"uid":140028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":