the U.S. commitment to democracy, human rights, and the rule of law at a time when these freedoms and Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy are being eroded through interference by the Chinese government and Communist Party.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecc.gov%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fcommissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a7c1fcf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7bb0f6a8df45cbdd3c2baebad53b81ea2f1aa77a","tid":1310191,"uid":41145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，你所講個三位<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國會議員</span></strong>係咪呢三位？有錯請更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(Washington, D.C)&mdash; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Representative Jim McGovern (D-MA)</span></span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Senator Marco Rubio (R-FL)</span></span></strong>, the Chair and Cochair respectively of the Congressional-Executive Commission on China (CECC), along with CECC Commissioner and former Chair, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Representative Chris Smith (R-NJ)</span></span></strong> today reintroduced the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, bicameral and bipartisan legislation that reaffirms the U.S. commitment to democracy, human rights, and the rule of law at a time when these freedoms and Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy are being eroded through interference by the Chinese government and Communist Party.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecc.gov%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fcommissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a7c1fcf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d5f90558eeb56a76149e037f313055f9f3c7499c","tid":1310191,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36588d8192d011842d24f71dca06271391d0ca72","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bb0f6a8df45cbdd3c2baebad53b81ea2f1aa77a","tid":1310191,"uid":41145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，你所講個三位<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國會議員</span></strong>係咪呢三位？有錯請更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(Washington, D.C)&mdash; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Representative Jim McGovern (D-MA)</span></span></strong> and <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Senator Marco Rubio (R-FL)</span></span></strong>, the Chair and Cochair respectively of the Congressional-Executive Commission on China (CECC), along with CECC Commissioner and former Chair, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Representative Chris Smith (R-NJ)</span></span></strong> today reintroduced the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, bicameral and bipartisan legislation that reaffirms the U.S. commitment to democracy, human rights, and the rule of law at a time when these freedoms and Hong Kong&rsquo;s autonomy are being eroded through interference by the Chinese government and Communist Party.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cecc.gov%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fcommissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a7c1fcf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cecc.gov/media-center/press-releases/commissioners-reintroduce-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n</span></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔該你幫推<br />\n但解釋一下<br />\n三封信<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係</span>寄比個三位議員的。係按寫信人的地址寄比當地其他議員（美國兩院總共535個），等多D議員知道香港宜家情況。就可以開始討論同多D 議員支持！因爲齋靠個三個議員 係唔會動議架！！"},{"pid":"11d07a59be09f8c1e6c54a028da67f14a4dc5339","tid":1310191,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d945e36a17b64403748df9946daadb6a971fbef","tid":1310191,"uid":269641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f6322b763eaf6ffd3a8a604ef3988b5d0e8e88b","tid":1310191,"uid":74363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實總議員同參議員分別要幾多人先可以move?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"無固定人數 睇committee chair。越多越有 noise。<br />\n<br />\n但其實政治依D野， 最後係一個利益交易。我地只能做到我地可以做嘅野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"Email 去committee chair <br />\n過左一個committee 應該仲有一個先上floor"},{"pid":"67d253b9b16e301a58c8de70ef37cbe194bfeeb3","tid":1310191,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bb0f6a8df45cbdd3c2baebad53b81ea2f1aa77a","tid":1310191,"uid":41145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:57:54.000Z","msg